          "name": "Dented Kettle Helm",
          "categoryId": "804u5339xhs9"
        },
        {
          "subtype": "Body Part",
          "side": "mundane",
          "tierId": null,
          "hasStack": true,
          "stack": 6,
          "fields": {
            "eay8cuxvxhs9": "The Severed Head of a brigand, surrounded by flies it draws the attention of humans just as well. The stink of death grows with every minute. May be worth a few coins to a Magistrate of Sheriff."
