          "stack": 1,
          "fields": {
            "gcauyfs4xhs9": "1500",
            "eay8cuxvxhs9": "A scrimshawed whalebone harpoon, engraved with thousands of deeply carved runes. The handle is made of a Welest fabric which resembles a flowing river, cool and soft. It conforms to the shape of the hand, flowing and dancing between the fingers elegantly."
